Author: Belarie
Text: This may not make you feel better, but since it’s from your own body it can’t make you gain weight, since you’re just ingesting your own matter, like if you ate your fingernail skin or something (gross but idk), it would of been on your body anyway, but now you’re digesting it  Also, since you’re sick, you’re burning more calories trying to cure your body of sickness AND digest the accidental phlegmy you swallowed. Even if it’s minute. Yay!....  Sorry if this was disgusting to read, but I hope it was reassuring, ED brains are weird :(
